=head1 NAME

 Summit

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Out of date.  Basecamp added reply by email functionality a couple years after this code was written.  It is here for educational purposes only.

 A qpsmtpd based plugin which accepts forwarded basecamp emails, grabs the url,
logs into basecamp and posts a comment which is located at the top of the
forwarded email and is ended with two linefeeds or carraige returns.

=cut